title: Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders DSM-5 (201
description:
The copy of the DSM-5 currently floating about (30MB) uses JBIG compression, which displays extremely slowly.  This file was created by reprocessing the existing file for improved size and performance.  Logical page numbering was added (for readers that support it), and several pages were edited for legibility (eg, pages with text within gray/black boxes).

PDF. OCR. Bookmarks.
